      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. You\u2019ll find it runs smoothly and looks great, making it perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. I've taken care of the essentials, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
